<p><b>High Commissioner and the Secretary-General 
</b></p>
<p><b>Promotion and protection of all human rights, civil, 
</b></p>
<p><b>political, economic, social and cultural rights, 
</b></p>
<p><b>including the right to development 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Report on creating and/or strengthening synergies and 
linkages on violence against women and girls 
</b></p>
<p><b>  Report of the Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for 
</b></p>
<p><b>Human Rights 
</b></p>
<p><i>Summary 
</i></p>
<p> Pursuant to Human Rights Council resolution 20/12, the following is a set of 
recommendations on synergies and linkages between the mechanisms of the Human Rights 
Council, and with other relevant intergovernmental processes on the issue of violence 
against women and girls. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>

